## Content Quality

**Do:**
- Explain concepts before using technical terms
- Use real-world examples and analogies
- Add visual breaks with horizontal rules (`---`)
- Test that all links work

**Don't:**
- Assume prior knowledge without context
- Use jargon without explanation
- Create walls of text without breaks
- Skip important setup steps





